race.description: Christmas Carols At Eagle Farm 20 Dec Mdn Hcp
race.comment: Tricky race to assess with a few of these facing the starter for the first time. ENJECTOR (2) is one of them but is sure to be well-educated out of the Freedman barn. Won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot and any push in betting must be noted. RED SAMOVAR (10) wasn't too far away here on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Capable of featuring prominently. TASSORATI (12) has been thereabouts in both starts to date and looks to be improving with racing. Progressive type nearing a win. FORGING AHEAD (3) strips fitter third-up from the break and may earn some minor money. MISHANI PRINCE (5) has placed three of his past four and looks one for the exotics players.
